'''Mehret Mandefro''' (wavutse 1977) ni Umunyetiyopiya-Umunyamerika utunganya firime / seri za televiziyo, umwanditsi, umuganga na antropropologue . <ref>https://www.carnegie.org/awards/honoree/mehret-mandefro/</ref> <ref>https://lailasnews.com/pavillon-afriques-joke-silva-kunle-afolayan-rita-dominic-cannes-film-festival/</ref> Ni umuyobozi w'itsinda rya Indaba Africa, akaba yarashinze ikigo cya Realness Institute <ref>https://variety.com/2020/film/news/sundance-rotterdam-realness-institute-african-producers-1234710821/</ref> akaba ari nawe washinze Truth Aid Media <ref>http://www.tadias.com/06/26/2020/ethiopian-filmmakers-abraham-gezahagne-and-yared-zeleke-selected-for-2020-realness-screenwriters-residency/</ref> akaba n'umwe mu bagize inama y'abajyanama mu Harvest Fund. <ref>https://www.forbes.com/sites/devinthorpe/2018/04/11/these-three-mds-have-a-prescription-for-curing-student-debt/?sh=1dc0bb8c428d</ref> Yahawe kandi igihembo cya Paul &amp;amp; Daisy Soros Fellowship kubanyamerika bashya (2001) maze muri 2007 yicara nkumwe mubantu 41 bazwi cyane muri [[Amerika]]. <ref>https://www.pdsoros.org/meet-the-fellows/mehret-mandefro</ref> <ref>http://www.payvand.com/news/07/feb/1298.html</ref> Muri 2016, yahawe icyubahiro na Carnegie Corporation ya New York nk'umwe mu Bimukira bakomeye bo muri [[Amerika]]. <ref>https://armenianweekly.com/2016/06/30/afeyan-carnegie/</ref>

== Ubuzima n'uburere ==
Mandefro yavukiye i [[Addis Ababa|Addis Abeba]], [[Etiyopiya|muri Etiyopiya]] mu 1977, akurira muri Alegizandiriya, muri Virijiniya, muri Amerika. Se, Ayalew Mandefro, yari Minisitiri w’ingabo muri Etiyopiya na nyina Tsedale K. Mandefro. Umuryango we wahungiye muri Amerika nyuma y’ubutegetsi bwa gikomunisiti bwa Etiyopiya bwagerageje kwica se. Yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya siyansi n’ikoranabuhanga rya Thomas Jefferson arangiza icyiciro cya mbere cya kaminuza n’ubuvuzi muri kaminuza ya Harvard . Yakomeje impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu buzima rusange bw’abaturage ku ishuri ry’i Londere ry’isuku n’ubuvuzi bwa Tropical nka Scholar ya Fulbright . Yasoje gahunda ya Robert Wood Johnson Foundation Health and Society Scholars Program muri kaminuza ya Pennsylvania yibanda ku mibereho y’ubuzima akomeza gukurikirana impamyabumenyi ya PhD muri Anthropologie y’umuco muri kaminuza ya Temple aho yarangirije igitabo cyerekeye ishingwa ry’ubuzima bw’Abanyamerika. politiki muri guverinoma ihuriweho na leta. <ref>http://www.healthandsocietyscholars.org/the-scholars/416641/1985</ref> Aragenda ku kumenyereza muri internal medicine muri Montefiore Medical Center na Albert Einstein College of Medicine aho bakurikirana ubushakashatsi ku ubusumbane SIDA mu bagore  <ref>http://www.tadias.com/03/08/2012/celebrating-international-womens-history-month-qa-with-dr-mehret-mandefro/</ref> <ref>https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/change-power-dynamics-relationships-article-1.264328</ref>

Mandefro kandi yari Umukozi wa White House mu butegetsi bwa Obama . <ref>http://www.tadias.com/06/14/2010/nbc%E2%80%99s-tom-brokaw-highlights-white-house-fellow-mehret-mandefro/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mandefro numwe mubahawe icyubahiro muri 2009 muri Black Girls Rock Awards, ahabwa igihembo cyumuganda.

Muri Werurwe 2014, yari umwe mu bagore bubashywe mu birori byo kwizihiza umunsi mpuzamahanga w’abagore mu mujyi wa New York, na WomenWerk. <ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2014/03/its-the-century-of-the-african-woman-womenwerk-celebrates-interational-womens-day-in-new-york/</ref> Muri 2014 kandi, yakoranye na firime ''Difret'', iyobowe na [[Zeresenay Berhane Mehari]] . <ref>{{Template:Cite web}}https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/difret-sundance-review-674060</ref> <ref>http://www.tadias.com/02/11/2014/tadias-interview-with-difret-director-and-producer/</ref> <ref>https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-sundance-difret-20140122-story.html</ref> <ref>https://www.jacksonville.com/article/20160311/NEWS/801244782</ref>

Yakoranye na firime Zeresenay Berhane ya 2019 yitwa,''Sweetness in the Belly'', hamwe na Adrian Sturges, Laura Bickford na Fiona Druckenmiller. <ref>http://www.tadias.com/04/11/2019/spotlight-mehret-mandefros-the-loving-generation-up-for-webby-award/</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, documentaire yayoboye  yise " ''The Loving Generation'' ", yatorewe igihembo cya Webby People Voice Award. <ref>https://scannain.com/featured/feature-irish-films-to-watch-out-for-in-2019/</ref> Iyi filime yemejwe ku mugaragaro ko izerekanwa ku rwego mpuzamahanga mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi  rya Toronto (TIFF). <ref>https://scannain.com/irish/abroad/tiff-19-irish-2/</ref>

Mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2019 ryabereye muri Palais Des Festivals, i Cannes, mu Bufaransa, yagiriye inama abakora amafilime yo muri Afurika kubaka ubufatanye bufatika bakorana, agaragaza ko ibindi bihugu bya Afurika bishobora kwigira kuri Nollywood kugira ngo biteze imbere mu nganda zabo. <ref>https://www.pmnewsnigeria.com/2019/05/21/movie-director-afolayan-decries-segregation-in-filmmaking-in-africa/</ref> <ref>https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/10-nollywood-stars-to-attend-the-cannes-film-festival-2019/8gxgksc</ref>

We, hamwe n’umuyobozi wa firime, Abraham Gezahagne, muri Gashyantare 2020 yari ahagarariye [[Etiyopiya]] muri Berlinale Africa Hub, aho yerekanaga amahirwe aboneka hamwe n’ibibazo byugarije inganda za firime na televiziyo mu gihugu. <ref>https://variety.com/2020/film/entertainment-industry/berlinale-2020-ethiopia-africa-hub-1203512155/</ref>

We, afatanije na Alicia Keys, Lacey Schwartz Delgado, Elliott Halpern na Elizabeth Trojian, umuyobozi mukuru bakoze documentaire,''How It Feels To Be Free'', ishingiye ku gitabo cya Ruth Feldstein,''How It Feels To Be Free: Black Women Entertainers and the Civil Rights Movement,'' ziyobowe na Yoruba Richen kandi zigomba kwerekanwa bwa mbere mu itumba 2021 na PBS na WNET . <ref>https://realscreen.com/2020/07/28/pbs-thirteen-prep-how-it-feels-to-be-free-doc-with-alicia-keys-yap-films/</ref> <ref>https://verysmartbrothas.theroot.com/10-thoughts-after-watching-the-loving-generation-docume-1823357499</ref>

